  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      A comparison of the effect of on demand treatment with a pectin-containing natural product
      (Aflurax) with that esomeprazole (Nexium)
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      A randomized, controlled, open trial comparing the symptomatic effect of a pectin-containing
      product (Aflurax) with that of esomeprazole (Nexium 20 mg) given on-demand for 6 weeks.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
